Package GTUCargoAutomation

Class CargoAutomation

java.lang.Object
GTUCargoAutomation.CargoAutomation
public class CargoAutomation
extends java.lang.Object
Represents a cargo automation. The automation system for a cargo company has users such as administrators, branch employees, transportation personnel and customers.
Author:
